descriptionHtml:
[i]My first upload to the nexus![/i]

I ended up making  a pretty good looking middle-aged woman.
[size=1]I don't really dig the typical "plastic" look seen around the Nexus, so yeah, she has those sexy flaws about her. (You're either into that sort of thing or you aren't)[/size]
Since there's not a lot of middle-aged women on here, I thought I'd share it.
She's a Nord, but may have a little Elven blood in her, who knows! ;-)

Please upload screenshots if you can and you use her!

INSTALLATION:
Put the file in the folder: Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

Requires:
SKSE[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]
RaceMenu[/url]
